      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% on quantity of interest (RHI) using at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three mesh levels (3.2M, 6.8M, 14.1M cells) evaluated. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 1.8% on RHI at the worst-case operating point (6 LPM / 3500 RPM). Mesh refinement ratio approximately 1.4 between levels."
