    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. GCI < 2%, output comparison within combined uncertainty bounds, and full operating envelope coverage collectively support an Accepted decision. The model revision from v3r1 to v3r2 (tip-clearance correction, 2025-11-03) was reviewed and assessed by the team as not materially affecting the validation dataset's applicability; the dataset's fluid property and boundary condition inputs remain valid for the revised geometry. The team acknowledges the dataVintage of the primary dataset predates the model revision date but judges the gap (approximately 3 weeks) and the nature of the change to be inconsequential to the credibility conclusion.",
